S.FORM: Pacidal Itiniay i Xincheng Cen no Hualien ko Pacidal a niyaro', 161 ko sa'osi no parod no loma', 398 ko sa'osi no tamdaw. 72% ko ka'aloman no Yincomin , polong han i, 285 ko tamdaw; o roma sato i, 28% ko ka'aloman no roma a finacadan, polong han i, 113 ko tamdaw. O pa-sin-to no ka'aloman no tamdaw no kasafinacadan i, ko Amis 52%, 撒奇拉雅族1%, Bunun 5%, Tayal 1%, Truku 9%, roma 3%.
